WeScrape is designed to be the most simple and most powerful web scraper you've ever used. No code required.

Launch the extension, click on elements and that's it ! You can now export your scraped data to CSV or Json. WeScrape also offer the possibility to automate your scraping on a recurring basis and connect your data to Zapier.

Create a free account on https://wescrape.co
